Package: openbahn
Type: Package
Title: Query the Deutsche Bahn Timetable API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Ottolinger", email = "philipp@ottolinger.de", "role" = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Philipp Ottolinger <philipp@ottolinger.de>
Description: This package queries the Deutsche Bahn Timetable API which covers the German long distance traffic. Each API endpoint is handled by its own function providing searches for locations, retrieval of arrival and departure boards as well as getting further details on specific journeys.
URL: https://github.com/ottlngr/openbahn
BugReports: http://github.com/ottlngr/openbahn/issues
References: http://data.deutschebahn.com/dataset/api-fahrplan
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: httr, jsonlite
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
